                     <interp inst="t18190421-117-person1268" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer of Hatton-garden. When the prisoner was apprehended I asked him what he had done with the rest of Gabb's things? he said he pledged the other coat at Aldgate - I went there and found it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190421-117-person1269">
                  RICHARD 
                  GABB
               <interp inst="t18190421-117-person1269" type="surname" value="GABB"></interp>
