                     <interp inst="t18190421-117-person1269" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The coats and waistcoats are mine. and are worth 4 l. together.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man gave them to me in the public-house.</p>
